components.name: SearchDropdownComponent
components.templateData:
<form class="searchDropdown">
  <mat-form-field
    class="searchDropdownField"
    [ngClass]="[status, isDisabled ? 'fieldDisable' : '']"
  >
    <mat-label class="dropdown">{{placeholder}}</mat-label>
    <input
      type="text"
      aria-label="Number"
      matInput
      [formControl]="myControl"
      [matAutocomplete]="auto"
      [attr.disabled]="isDisabled == false ? null : isDisabled"
    />
    <mat-autocomplete
      #auto="matAutocomplete"
      (optionSelected)="handleChanges($event.option.value)"
    >
      <mat-option
        matTooltip="{{option.label.length > textLimit ? option.label : '' }}"
        *ngFor="let option of filteredOptions$ | async"
        [value]="option.label"
      >
        {{option.label}}
      </mat-option>
    </mat-autocomplete>
    <mat-hint class="toaster toaster-background"
      >{{ message }}</mat-hint
    >
  </mat-form-field>
</form>
